text:
Aben Builders
Metallstr. 211
07685 Konstanz
Germany
12. July 2023
Advance Payment Guarantee No. 404BGI554545
Dear Sirs,
We have been informed that a contract, hereinafter "Underlying Contract", has been
concluded between you and Anglo Builders, Metall Street 13, 40423 Fischen, Germany
hereinafter "Principal", on 01.06.2023 under ref. No. 86423232 for the delivery of one ton of
red bricks at a total price of USD 20.000.000,00 and that the Underlying Contract stipulates
that an advance payment in the amount of 10% of the total price be effected against an
Advance Payment Guarantee
This being premised, we, Goods Bank, Frankfurt, hereby irrevocably undertake to pay you
without delay on your first written demand for payment an amount up to
USD 2000.000,00
(in words: USD two million)
provided your demand for payment is simultaneously supported by your written statement
(whether in the demand itself or in a separate document(s) accompanying the demand and
referred to in it) stating
a) that the Principal is in breach of his obligation(s) under the Underlying Contract, and
b) the respect in which the Principal is in breach, and
c) that the obligation(s) in respect of which the Principal is in breach is/are covered by
the present guarantee and that you are therefore entitled to demand repayment of
the advance payment up to the amount of the demand for payment.
This guarantee shall enter into effect if and to the extent the advance payment of USD
2000.000,00 is credited in full without reserve to Principal's account no. 111 289654 held
with us in Frankfurt, IBAN DE98 2544 2598 5543 3655 65 with reference to this guarantee, at
his free disposal.
This guarantee shall expire, even if this document is not returned, on 20. December 2035,
and shall then be null and void, if and to the extent that no demand under this guarantee in
accordance with its conditions has reached us in Frankfurt by the end of that day.
This guarantee is freely transferable.
This guarantee is subject to Russian Law.
Goods Bank
